inite family of $2$-$\\mathcal{NM}$-closed\ngraphs, color-connected, with an alternating cycle factor, and with no\nalternating Hamiltonian cycle.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Oct 2018 04:45:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 26 Apr 2019 02:11:05 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 16 May 2019 22:51:58 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 10 Jun 2019 02:10:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-04"}
