nificant improvement on\ncomputational efficiency compared with UGKS and DSMC, especially in the near\ncontinuum flow regime.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Oct 2018 12:48:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 Oct 2018 02:03:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-12"}
