ravel new insights into cardiac physiology and could\nenable a novel standardized methodology to study MV-LV hemodynamic coupling and\nassociation to cardiac function in health and disease.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Oct 2018 14:47:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 Oct 2018 00:49:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-12"}
